 What's the settlement cost for next month from the businesses in the department store? 

6
00:00:14,265 --> 00:00:16,835
 - 140 billion won ($140M), Ma'am. 
 - Make them into postdated checks. 

7
00:00:16,835 --> 00:00:18,376
 - Sorry? 
 - I'm going to invest 

8
00:00:18,376 --> 00:00:20,975
 those 140 billion won ($140M) into New Data Technology. 

9
00:00:20,975 --> 00:00:22,176
 CEO Jin, that's the department store's... 

10
00:00:22,176 --> 00:00:26,076
 I am Soonyang Department Store, and Soonyang Department Store is me! 

11
00:00:26,076 --> 00:00:27,846
What's going on? That is Director Im's voice.

12
00:00:27,846 --> 00:00:30,385
- Director Im? Why? 
 - I have no idea.

13
00:00:30,385 --> 00:00:32,585
Can anyone reach Director Im right now?

14
00:00:32,585 --> 00:00:35,255
This recording was sent to the Prosecutors' Office

15
00:00:35,255 --> 00:00:39,126
by Ms. Im Myeong Sook, the former director of finance.

16
00:00:40,190 --> 00:00:43,193
That was your voice, right?

17
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:47,672
So she secretly recorded our conversations? Director Im did?

18
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,844
Since when?

19
00:00:50,844 --> 00:00:55,172
I believe this clearly proves that you are indeed guilty of embezzlement.

20
00:01:00,052 --> 00:01:02,512
The false tip didn't come from Miracle.

21
00:01:03,222 --> 00:01:05,883
It came from you, CEO Jin.

22
00:01:13,893 --> 00:01:16,092
   

23
00:01:18,330 --> 00:01:19,772
As for CEO Jin,

24
00:01:19,772 --> 00:01:23,573
I'm afraid the prosecutor's investigation of her embezzlement charges cannot be avoided.

25
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:27,972
Did you say the person who handed over evidence to the prosecutors

26
00:01:27,972 --> 00:01:31,012
is a director at the department store?

27
00:01:31,012 --> 00:01:33,613
I apologize, Sir.

28
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:41,453
When a dog bites its master,

29
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,593
whose fault is it?

30
00:01:48,593 --> 00:01:51,063
Try all you want. Five years? Ten years?

31
00:01:51,063 --> 00:01:53,633
No. Even if I have to rot in prison for 50 years,

32
00:01:53,633 --> 00:01:57,843
I will never hand over my shares to you.

33
00:02:00,410 --> 00:02:05,613
Then I guess you'll end up rotting in prison, and the department store stock will become worthless.

34
00:02:05,613 --> 00:02:10,682
If you fail to pay off the promissory notes this month, the department store will go bankrupt.

35
00:02:10,682 --> 00:02:16,592
Then the creditors and banks will be the ones liquidating the subsidiaries that are of any worth.

36
00:02:16,592 --> 00:02:21,493
Do you think Grandfather would accept you back if you lose even the subsidiaries?

37
00:02:21,493 --> 00:02:25,102
Thanks to you, Uncle Chang Je's political career would be over too.

38
00:02:25,102 --> 00:02:27,372
Do you think he'll welcome you back?

39
00:02:29,170 --> 00:02:33,143
This is your last chance. Hand over your department store shares.

40
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:38,512
Then I'll let you keep your dignity as Chairman Jin Yang Cheol's only daughter.

41
00:02:38,512 --> 00:02:41,253
The prosecutors making you pose in front of the cameras...

42
00:02:41,253 --> 00:02:44,482
I do not want Grandfather to see that.

43
00:02:47,692 --> 00:02:51,062
Hey, why me? Why Soonyang Department Store?

44
00:02:51,062 --> 00:02:53,992
