45
00:02:57,030 --> 00:03:01,202
You taught me.

46
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:09,103
 Don't you dare delude yourself into thinking that you can be a rightful heir. 

47
00:03:09,103 --> 00:03:10,642
 You guys... 

48
00:03:12,610 --> 00:03:18,552
 are different from us. 

49
