168
00:13:58,223 --> 00:14:00,593
This is the reason you suddenly showed up

169
00:14:00,593 --> 00:14:04,402
out of nowhere and gave me a tip.

170
00:14:04,402 --> 00:14:07,133
From beginning to end,

171
00:14:07,133 --> 00:14:09,733
