172
00:14:10,373 --> 00:14:12,973
You knew from the beginning

173
00:14:14,642 --> 00:14:17,782
that I didn't tip you off for the sake of law and order.

174
00:14:17,782 --> 00:14:18,983
- Hey, that's... 
 - "Let me use..."

175
00:14:18,983 --> 00:14:21,953
"a third-generation heir to realize justice."

176
00:14:21,953 --> 00:14:25,623
That's what you said. Don't you remember?

177
00:14:26,182 --> 00:14:30,363
Hey, why are you so good with... You really do have a way with words.

