00:14:45,402 --> 00:14:47,503
The Seo Min Yeong I know.

183
00:14:47,503 --> 00:14:50,013
Don't make that face.

184
00:14:51,213 --> 00:14:54,753
Those eyes and that face, as if you know everything about me.

185
00:14:55,453 --> 00:14:57,713
Don't do that.

186
00:14:59,052 --> 00:15:02,353
I nearly bought

187
00:15:02,353 --> 00:15:04,393
