00:15:10,963 --> 00:15:13,032
When my boss told me I'd never be able to return

190
00:15:13,032 --> 00:15:16,372
to the Central Office if I got transferred because of this,

191
00:15:16,372 --> 00:15:18,103
I couldn't even say anything

192
00:15:18,103 --> 00:15:20,613
