195
00:15:26,812 --> 00:15:29,753
I'm so cowardly and materialistic.

196
00:15:31,123 --> 00:15:33,682
Do you think I'll be a good prosecutor?

197
00:15:37,463 --> 00:15:40,763
I bet you have no idea how sly I can be.

198
00:15:40,763 --> 00:15:43,833
When they reassigned the case to someone else to reprimand me,

199
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:47,133
everyone else in the office was worried about me.

200
00:15:48,302 --> 00:15:52,973
But the truth is, I was so relieved

201
00:15:52,973 --> 00:15:56,672
