202
00:15:56,672 --> 00:15:59,512
how cowardly and servile I was

203
00:16:00,252 --> 00:16:02,452
in front of my boss.

204
00:16:16,632 --> 00:16:19,503
Why are you telling me all this?

205
00:16:24,543 --> 00:16:26,173
I wonder, too.

206
00:16:27,743 --> 00:16:31,042
