From the very beginning...

208
00:16:34,953 --> 00:16:38,623
I should get going before I give more away.

209
00:16:40,823 --> 00:16:43,663
I won't be a great prosecutor,

210
00:16:43,663 --> 00:16:46,093
which means

211
00:16:46,093 --> 00:16:48,493
you lied to me.

