00:17:29,933 --> 00:17:32,772
- My gosh. 
 - Seriously?

214
00:17:32,772 --> 00:17:34,072
Oh, my.

215
00:17:34,072 --> 00:17:36,972
- I can't believe this. 
 - Me, neither.

216
00:17:36,972 --> 00:17:40,583
