♫  I am falling into a deeper place  ♫

954
01:12:31,430 --> 01:12:36,350
♫  I’m afraid I won’t be able  ♫

955
01:12:36,350 --> 01:12:40,630
♫  to return to my rightful place anymore  ♫

956
01:12:40,630 --> 01:12:43,430
♫   In the end  ♫

957
01:12:45,370 --> 01:12:50,310
♫   I can't breathe, no, I can't breathe  ♫

958
01:12:50,310 --> 01:12:52,940
♫   In the end  ♫

